<ul>
<li>是否疑问句</li>
</ul>
<p>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Has he signed the contract?</p>
<p>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;在疑问句之前加if/whether并将词序更改为主+谓,其用途为:</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">主语</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">Whether she has signed the contract doesn't matter.</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">be后作补语</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">The question is whether she has signed the contract.</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">作动词的宾语</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">I want to know whether/if she has signed the contract.</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">作介词的宾语</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">I'm concerned about whether he has signed the contract.&#160;</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">&#160;</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">如果句子开关是从句,则必须用whether</p>
<p style=" margin-left: 40.0px;">在be/介词后,必须用whether</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<ul>
<li>由带疑问词的疑问句引出的名词从句</li>
</ul>
<p>How soon will we know the result?</p>
<p>疑问词+词序的改变,可以起名词从句的作用.用途:</p>
<p>When he did it is mystry.</p>
<p>The question is when he did it.</p>
<p>I wonder when he did it.</p>
<p>It depends on when he did it.</p>
<p>I'm interested in when he did it.</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>what==the things that</p>
<p>What matter most is good health.</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
